originalText.text:
I have found Dr Greenberg to be generous with her talent and time on Quora. She has helped me personally understand attributes that are both helpful and harmful in personal and professional situations. She's a self-disciplined therapist, and a very patient one. She exhibits concern for her patients and has the training to observe and forbear the kind of treatment patients may unknowingly exhibit because they are sitting in her office for a reason.
If you're looking for sympathy I would suggest calling a friend. If you were looking to improve your own insights, life and understanding, I would suggest exploring treatment from Dr Greenberg and listening to her explanations and suggestions to improve and change your life.
